<MudText Typo="Typo.h3" GutterBottom="true">Welcome to Dawnshard</MudText>
<MudText Typo=Typo.h5 Class="mb-4">Dawnshard is a server emulator project aimed at enabling continued play of Dragalia Lost.</MudText>
<MudText Class="mb-6">Ever since the official servers were discontinued in November 2022, Dawnshard has been in development as a fan-led reimplementation of the game.</MudText>
